        "Region": 3,
        "CharacterDialogInfo_List": [
          {
            "CharacterId": 16007,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1600701,
            "DisplayOrder": 270,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8000,
            "LocalizeKR": "후우, 아무 것도 보이지\n않을 정도의 엄청난\n눈보라였네요……",
            "LocalizeJP": "ふぅ、何も見えなく\nなるほどすごい\n吹雪でしたね……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_01_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 16007,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1600701,
            "DisplayOrder": 280,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 4750,
            "LocalizeKR": "선생님도 겉옷을\n벗는 게 어떠신가요?",
            "LocalizeJP": "先生も、上着を\n脱いではいかがですか？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_02_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 16007,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1600701,
            "DisplayOrder": 290,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 7000,
            "LocalizeKR": "젖은 옷을 그대로 입고 있으면\n감기에 걸릴 수도 있다고요?",
            "LocalizeJP": "そのまま濡れた服を着ていると、\n風邪を引いてしまいますよ？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 16007,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1600701,
            "DisplayOrder": 300,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 9500,
            "LocalizeKR": "……선생님?\n무슨 일 있으신가요.\n뭔가, 신경 쓰이는 일이라도?",
            "LocalizeJP": "……先生？\nどうかされましたか、\n何か気になることでも？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_03_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 16007,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1600701,
            "DisplayOrder": 310,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 4850,
            "LocalizeKR": "그 표정은, 혹시……",
            "LocalizeJP": "その表情、もしかして……",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_04_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 16007,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1600701,
            "DisplayOrder": 320,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 8500,
            "LocalizeKR": "조금 전의 연설로는 부족해서,\n체리노 회장님의 이야기를 더\n듣고 싶어지신 건가요?",
            "LocalizeJP": "先ほどの演説では足りず、\nもっとチェリノ会長の\nお話が聞きたいのですか？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 16007,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1600701,
            "DisplayOrder": 330,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 4150,
            "LocalizeKR": "이런 타이밍이기도 하고,\n마침 잘 되었네요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "こんなタイミングですし、\nちょうど良いですね。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle5",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_05_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 16007,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1600701,
            "DisplayOrder": 340,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 9000,
            "LocalizeKR": "그럼 눈이 그칠 때까지,\n함께 체리노 회장님의\n위대함에 대해\n이야기를 나누도록 하죠!",
            "LocalizeJP": "では雪が止むまで、\n一緒にチェリノ会長の\n偉大さについて\n語り合うとしましょう♪",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle5",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
